trans-unit.source:
Type: basic
Path restriction: find/{address}
Response code: 303 See Other
Response redirect URL: https://www.google.com/maps?q={address}
---
Result: domain.tld/find/Switzerland → https://www.google.com/maps?q=Switzerland

trans-unit.target:
Typ: einfach
